  'en',
  'onion-boil-recipe',
  'Onion Boil Recipe – Cozy Winter Onion Soup',
  'This comforting onion boil recipe transforms simple onions into a rich, savory broth that feels like a warm hug on cold winter days.',
  'The onion boil is an underrated classic that sits somewhere between onion soup and vegetable soup. As the onions simmer, they soften and release natural sweetness, creating a deeply comforting broth with very little effort.',
  E'When winter hits and all you want is something warm, simple, and soothing, the onion boil quietly steals the show. It may sound humble, but don''t underestimate the power of onions slowly simmered into a fragrant, savory broth.\n\nThis onion boil recipe has been making waves as the ultimate winter comfort food. Think of it as onion soup''s laid-back cousin: fewer steps, fewer ingredients, but all the cozy vibes. It''s the kind of meal that warms your hands, your belly, and your mood all at once.',
  E'Serve this onion boil hot, preferably in a big bowl you can wrap your hands around. It''s perfect as a light dinner, a starter, or even a comforting lunch on cold days.\n\nPair it with crusty bread or enjoy it on its own as one of those warm meals for cold days that proves simple food can still be deeply satisfying.',
  '[{"title": "Ingredients", "items": [{"quantity": "4", "unit": "large", "name": "onions", "note": "peeled and halved"}, {"quantity": "1.5", "unit": "L", "name": "vegetable broth", "note": ""}, {"quantity": "2", "unit": "tbsp", "name": "butter", "note": ""}, {"quantity": "1", "unit": "tbsp", "name": "olive oil", "note": ""}, {"quantity": "1", "unit": "tsp", "name": "garlic powder", "note": ""}, {"quantity": "1/2", "unit": "tsp", "name": "dried thyme", "note": ""}, {"quantity": "", "unit": "", "name": "salt", "note": "to taste"}, {"quantity": "", "unit": "", "name": "black pepper", "note": "to taste"}]}]',
  '[{"step": 1, "title": "Prepare the onions", "content": "Peel the onions and cut them in half from top to bottom. Keeping them large helps them hold their shape while slowly softening in the broth.", "tip": "Use yellow onions for the best balance of sweetness and savoriness."}, {"step": 2, "title": "Build flavor", "content": "In a large pot, melt the butter with olive oil over medium heat. Add the onions cut-side down and let them lightly caramelize for a few minutes to boost natural sweetness.", "tip": "Do not rush this step—gentle browning adds depth to the onion boil."}, {"step": 3, "title": "Add the broth", "content": "Pour in the vegetable broth, making sure the onions are mostly submerged. Sprinkle in garlic powder, thyme, salt, and pepper.", "tip": "Vegetable broth keeps this recipe light, but chicken broth also works."}, {"step": 4, "title": "Simmer gently", "content": "Bring the pot to a gentle boil, then reduce to a simmer. Cook uncovered for about 35–40 minutes until the onions are very tender and the broth is deeply flavored.", "tip": "The longer it simmers, the closer it gets to a rich onion soup."}, {"step": 5, "title": "Serve warm", "content": "Taste and adjust seasoning if needed. Serve hot in bowls with plenty of broth and soft onions.", "tip": "Great with toasted bread or as a base for onion soup mix recipe ideas."}]',
  'Onion Boil Recipe | Cozy Winter Onion Soup',
  'Discover this cozy onion boil recipe, a simple winter meal made with tender onions and savory broth. Perfect for cold days and comfort cravings.',
  '[{"question_fr": "Peut-on préparer cette recette à l''avance?", "answer_fr": "Oui, l''onion boil se conserve très bien et est encore meilleur réchauffé.", "question_en": "Can this recipe be made ahead?", "answer_en": "Yes, onion boil stores well and tastes even better when reheated."}, {"question_fr": "Quelle est la différence avec une soupe à l''oignon?", "answer_fr": "L''onion boil est plus simple, sans farine ni fromage, mais tout aussi réconfortant.", "question_en": "What''s the difference between onion boil and onion soup?", "answer_en": "Onion boil is simpler, without flour or cheese, but just as comforting."}, {"question_fr": "Peut-on ajouter d''autres légumes?", "answer_fr": "Oui, carottes ou céleri se marient très bien avec cette soupe.", "question_en": "Can other vegetables be added?", "answer_en": "Yes, carrots or celery pair very well with this soup."}]',
  NOW()
FROM recipes
WHERE slug = 'bouillon-oignon-reconfortant';
